==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Untrue
<hw>Un*true"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not true;
false; contrary to the fact; <as>as, the story is
<ex>untrue</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not faithful; inconstant; false; disloyal.</def>
<rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Untrue</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Untrue
<hw>Un*true</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>Untruly.</def> <mark>[Obs. or
Poetic]</mark> <rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Untruism</ent>⟦br⟧
